{"type":"message","id":"9628197e","parentId":"91bedbda","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:12:13.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I have all the information I need. Now I'll create:\n\n1. `error.tsx` - Global error component (must be a client component)\n2. `not-found.tsx` - Global not-found component\n\nBoth should follow the existing design patterns (dark theme, glassmorphism, Tailwind styling).\n\nLet me also check one of the existing page components to understand the styling patterns better.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now I'll create the missing error components. Let me create the global `error.tsx` and `not-found.tsx` files:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_6Cijo2HbenkcGuZh3Cc3mj2Y","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"'use client'\n\nimport { useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'\nimport { AlertTriangle, RefreshCw, Home } from 'lucide-react'\nimport Link from 'next/link'\n\nexport default function GlobalError({\n  error,\n  reset,\n}: {\n  error: Error & { digest?: string }\n  reset: () => void\n}) {\n  useEffect(() => {\n    // Log the error to an error reporting service\n    console.error('Global error:', error)\n  }, [error])\n\n  return (\n    <html lang=\"en\">\n      <body className=\"bg-[#0a0a0a] text-white min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4\">\n        <div className=\"glass rounded-xl p-8 max-w-md w-full text-center space-y-6\">\n          <div className=\"flex justify-center\">\n            <div className=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center\">\n              <AlertTriangle className=\"w-8 h-8 text-red-400\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n            <h1 className=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">\n              Something went wrong\n            </h1>\n            <p className=\"text-sm text-white/60\">\n              An unexpected error occurred. Please try again or return home.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          {error.message && (\n            <div className=\"bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 rounded-lg p-3 text-left\">\n              <p className=\"text-xs text-red-400 font-mono break-all\">\n                {error.message}\n              </p>\n              {error.digest && (\n                <p className=\"text-xs text-red-400/60 font-mono mt-1\">\n                  Error ID: {error.digest}\n                </p>\n              )}\n            </div>\n          )}\n\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center\">\n            <Button\n              onClick={reset}\n              variant=\"default\"\n              className=\"bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white border-0\"\n            >\n              <RefreshCw className=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" />\n              Try Again\n            </Button>\n            <Link href=\"/\" passHref>\n              <Button\n                variant=\"outline\"\n                className=\"border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 text-white\"\n              >\n                <Home className=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" />\n                Go Home\n              </Button>\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </body>\n    </html>\n  )\n}\n","file_path":"skills/mission-control-v2/app/error.tsx"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_myAwVeX1sNVzE6giNkUifUCc","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import Link from 'next/link'\nimport { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'\nimport { FileQuestion, Home, ArrowLeft } from 'lucide-react'\n\nexport default function NotFound() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0a] text-white flex items-center justify-center p-4\">\n      <div className=\"glass rounded-xl p-8 max-w-md w-full text-center space-y-6\">\n        <div className=\"flex justify-center\">\n          <div className=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center\">\n            <FileQuestion className=\"w-8 h-8 text-white/60\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n          <h1 className=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">\n            Page Not Found\n          </h1>\n          <p className=\"text-sm text-white/60\">\n            The page you&apos;re looking for doesn&apos;t exist or has been moved.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center\">\n          <Link href=\"/\" passHref>\n            <Button\n              variant=\"default\"\n              className=\"bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white border-0\"\n            >\n              <Home className=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" />\n              Go Home\n            </Button>\n          </Link>\n          <Button\n            variant=\"outline\"\n            className=\"border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 text-white\"\n            onClick={() => window.history.back()}\n          >\n            <ArrowLeft className=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" />\n            Go Back\n          </Button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n","file_path":"skills/mission-control-v2/app/not-found.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":1004,"output":1262,"cacheRead":14848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17114,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774213917232}}
