{"type":"message","id":"01468f33","parentId":"b592d1a5","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:14:05.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All files are in place. Let me provide a summary of all the fixes made.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"All error components are now in place. Here's a summary of the fixes:\n\n## ✅ Fixed Error Components\n\n### Created Files:\n1. **`app/error.tsx`** - Global error boundary for the app directory\n   - Handles client-side errors with a retry button\n   - Shows error message and digest ID\n   - Styled with glassmorphism to match the app design\n\n2. **`app/not-found.tsx`** - Global 404 page\n   - Handles unmatched routes\n   - Includes \"Go Home\" and \"Go Back\" buttons\n   - Consistent dark theme styling\n\n3. **`app/global-error.tsx`** - Root-level error handler\n   - Catches errors that occur in the root layout\n   - Critical error UI with page refresh option\n\n### Fixed Route Handler Issues:\n4. **`app/api/docs/[id]/route.ts`** - Fixed async params\n   - Changed `params: { id: string }` to `params: Promise<{ id: string }>`\n   - Added `await params` for Next.js 14+ compatibility\n   - Removed unused `nanoid` import\n\n5. **`app/api/tasks/[id]/route.ts`** - Fixed async params\n   - Updated all three handlers (GET, PATCH, DELETE) to use `Promise<{ id: string }>`\n\n6. **`app/api/agents/route.ts`** - Removed incorrect PATCH handler\n   - The PATCH handler was expecting params on a non-dynamic route (`/api/agents`)\n   - This was causing the \"missing required error components\" error\n\n### Root Cause:\nThe main issue was the **route handlers using the old params format** in Next.js 14+. Dynamic route segments now return a Promise for params that must be awaited. The incorrect PATCH handler in `/api/agents/route.ts` was also contributing to the error."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":265,"output":390,"cacheRead":30976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774214038453}}
